title: LeBron James and the Los Angeles Lakers are the 2020 NBA Champions | Real Ones
description:
Logan and Raja go live right after LeBron James and the Los Angeles Lakers win the 2020 NBA championship to talk about Game 6 and how this win impacts the legacies of all involved.

Hosts: Logan Murdock and Raja Bell
